   such permissions.

4. DATA LOSS: Cache and temporary file deletion is permanent. The dry-run
   mode is provided to preview operations before execution.

5. SYSTEM STABILITY: While safety measures are implemented, users should
   ensure system stability by testing in dry-run mode first.

By using this software, you acknowledge that you understand these risks
and agree to use the software at your own discretion and responsibility.